HTML -> View
TS -> Logic
CSS -> Design

Angular Components

Angular apps are built using Components

Component has 3 parts
HTML -> UI
Typescript -> Logic
CSS -> Design

Component is reusable
We can use it multiple times

> ng generate component component-name

Custom component tag
<app-component-name>

Interpolation connects ts to HTML
{{variable}}

Project Structure

src -> main app
app -> components folder
node_modules -> liabraries
angular.json -> project settings




